Class Component<P extends Page>

java.lang.Object
com.github.epadronu.dwalin.core.Component<P>
Type Parameters:
P - the type of page this component will be linked to
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.codeborne.selenide.SelenideElement, AbstractionLayer, org.openqa.selenium.interactions.Locatable, org.openqa.selenium.SearchContext, org.openqa.selenium.TakesScreenshot, org.openqa.selenium.WebElement, org.openqa.selenium.WrapsDriver, org.openqa.selenium.WrapsElement
public abstract non-sealed class Component<P extends Page> extends Object implements AbstractionLayer, com.codeborne.selenide.SelenideElement

Models a re-usable interface component that can be present multiple times in one or more pages.
